===============================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                                   |NAME    |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |LIMIT                                      |        |0       |15          |
|1 |└─PX COORDINATOR MERGE SORT                |        |1       |15          |
|2 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR                     |:EX10002|1       |13          |
|3 |    └─SORT                                 |        |1       |12          |
|4 |      └─HASH GROUP BY                      |        |1       |12          |
|5 |        └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR                |        |12      |12          |
|6 |          └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)      |:EX10001|12      |11          |
|7 |            └─HASH GROUP BY                |        |12      |7           |
|8 |              └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |12      |6           |
|9 |                └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)|:EX10000|12      |5           |
|10|                  └─HASH GROUP BY          |        |12      |1           |
|11|                    └─EXPANSION            |        |4       |1           |
|12|                      └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR  |        |1       |1           |
|13|                        └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |llm10   |1       |1           |
===============================================================================
